data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning residence offers the epitome of comfor and luxury. Step inside to discover new hardwood floors on main level, a spacious 2 story great room, where natural light floods through expansive windows, creating an inviting atmosphere for gatherings or relaxation. The updated kitchen boasts modern appliances, drawers to organize cutlery, and ample cabinet space. Whether you're hosting a dinner party or enjoying a casual meal with family, this kitchen will impress. Downstairs a full basement awaits your personal touch, already stubbed for a bathroom, offering endless possibilities for additional living space, entertainment or storage. Outside, escape to your own private oasis on the screened deck and additional larger deck. Community amenities include swim/tennis. Located near dining, shopping and I85 in a top rated school district. For peace of mind, an HVAC/Plumbing service  warranty is paid through 2025 with Coolray. OPEN HOUSE SUNDAY APRIL 7 2-4PM. COME SEE THIS AMAZING HOME!!
